(252, 1, '2017-06-03 04:36:23', '2017-06-03 04:36:23', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Steps to install visual studio code:\r\n1. Download visual studio code.\r\n2. Extract the zip file.\r\n3. Click install.\r\n4. Then click next button.\r\n5. Then click I accept terms and conditions, then click next button.\r\n6. Click ok button.\r\n7. Now the visual studio code will be installing successfully.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Steps to install .net frame work\r\n1. Download .net framework.\r\n2. Extract the zip file.\r\n3. Click install.\r\n4. Then click next button.\r\n5. Then click I accept terms and conditions, then click next button.\r\n6. Click ok button.\r\n7. Now the .net frame work will be installing successfully.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Steps to install nodejs and npm plug-in</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">1. Download nodejs\r\n2. Extract the zip file.\r\n3. Click install.\r\n4. Then click next button.\r\n5. Select npm.\r\n6. Click ok button.\r\n7. Then the nodejs and npm will be installing successfully.\r\n8. Open command prompt.\r\n9. Select specific folder.\r\n10. Type npm install -g typescript, then typescript will be installed successfully.\r\n11. Type node –v, it will displays the version\r\n12. Then type npm –v, it displays the version\r\n13. Then type tsc –v, it displays the version</p>', 'steps to install typescript', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'steps-to-install-typescript', '', '', '2017-06-03 04:38:11', '2017-06-03 04:38:11', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=252', 0, 'post', '', 0),
