(286, 1, '2017-08-04 05:04:57', '2017-08-04 05:04:57', 'Jharkhand SSC notified about new recruitment drive open in July/ August 2017. According to notification total 3019 new jobs open for Police Sub Inspector. Candidate who are graduate can submit their name online through official site only. The selection of SI will done by JSSC (recruitment cell) through written test and personal interview. Apply online from 15-July-2017 to 13-Aug-2017.\r\n\r\n<strong>Total Number of Vacancies:</strong> 3019\r\n\r\n<strong>Post Name</strong>: Police Sub Inspector\r\n\r\n<strong>Educational Qualification</strong>: Aspirant interested in JSSC Police Sub Inspector Recruitment 2017 2018 should have Graduate in any stream such as Arts / Commerce / Science or any other.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Fee Charges</strong>: Fee is non refundable, category wise details given below:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>General / OBC: Rs. 460/- (Rupee four hundred sixty only)</li>\r\n 	<li>SC/ST: Rs. 115/- (Rupee one hundred fifteen only)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>How to Apply Online</strong>\r\n\r\nJharkhand Staff Selection Commission has started application process for 3019 Police Sub Inspector vacancies. The commission has own online registration system to collect application details online, so all desirous candidate may reach to www.jssc.in website and by using the online application system submit form online between the dates 15-July to 13-Aug-2017.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.jssc.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Apply Online</strong></a>\r\n\r\nhttp://www.jssc.in/\r\n\r\n<strong>Important Dates</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Opening Date of Online Gateway:<strong> 15-July-2017</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Closing Date: <strong>13-Aug-2017</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Last Date to Pay Fee Charges: <strong>14-Aug-2017</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Last Date to Upload Photo &amp; Sign: <strong>16-Aug-2017</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'JSSC Recruitment 2017  – 3019 Police Sub Inspector',