(288, 1, '2017-08-04 05:21:04', '2017-08-04 05:21:04', 'Government of Madhya Pradesh given permission to start application process for the post of  Sub Inspector in various Department.  MP Professional Examination Board released application registration and examination dates to fill 611 SI. Apply online for SI from 01-Aug-2017 to 30-Aug-2017.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Total Number of Vacancies</strong>: 611</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Post Name: </strong>Sub Inspector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Educational Qualification</strong>: Graduate form recognized University OR Graduate in Physics, Chemistry &amp; Mathematics  form recognized University OR 3 years Diploma in Mechanical/Electronics.\r\n\r\n<strong>Age Limit</strong> : Lower &amp; Upper age limit is 18 to 25 years as on 01.01.2018.\r\n\r\n<strong>Selection Process</strong> : The selection will be made on the basis of Written Examination &amp; Interview.\r\n\r\n<strong>Application Fee :</strong> Candidates applying online have to pay Rs. 500/-  for General category candidates and Rs. 250/- for SC/ST and OBC candidates of MP and Rs.70/- for MP Online Portal Fee for all candidates fee can be pay through through MP Online (Kiosk)/ Net Banking/ Credit card/ Debit Card.\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Apply :</strong> Interested Candidates may apply online through www.vyapam.nic.in or www.mponline.gov.in from 01.08.2017 to 30.08.2017\r\n\r\n<strong>Important Dates to Remember :</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Opening Date of Registration : </strong>01-Aug-2017</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Closing Date of Online Gateway:</strong> 30-Aug-2017</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Starting Date for Making Corrections in Submitted Application Form : </strong>01-Aug-2017</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Closing Date for Making Corrections in Submitted Application Form : </strong>30-Aug-2017</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Date of Written Exam : </strong>22-Oct-2017 &amp; 29-Oct-2017</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Vyapam Sub Inspector Recruitment 2017', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vyapam-