(291, 1, '2017-08-04 06:38:41', '2017-08-04 06:38:41', '<strong>Upcoming Jobs</strong>: Exclusive news from Bihar. As per trusted sources CSBC, Bihar Police is now ready with recruitment notification for the year 2017 – 2018. This time decided to recruit huge number of Constable. This is preliminary information and we are waiting for the official notification.\r\n\r\n<strong>Updates 30th July 2017</strong>: Now the wait is over, Bihar Constable Vacancy 2017-18 notification released by Central Selection Board of Constable at their authorized website i.e. www.csbc.bih.nic.in.   Total 9900 jobs open for the post of Constable.\r\n\r\n<strong>Total Number of Vacancies</strong>: 9900\r\n\r\n<strong>Post Name: </strong>Constable\r\n\r\n<strong>Salary Offered: </strong>Rs. 5200-20200/-\r\n\r\n<strong>Official Portal</strong>: www.csbc.bih.nic.in\r\n\r\n<strong>Posting:</strong> Bihar\r\n\r\n<strong>Educational Qualification</strong>: Candidate who willing to claim should have 10+2 passed certificate issued by recognized school education board.\r\n\r\n<strong>Age Limit:</strong> The date for calculating cut off age is 1st June 2017\r\n\r\n<strong>Lower limit</strong>: 18 years for all categories\r\n\r\n<strong>Upper limit</strong>: 25 years for General, 28 years for OBC and 30 years for SC/ST.\r\n\r\n<strong>Important Dates</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Opening date of CSBC Gateway: <strong>31st July 2017</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Closing Date of CSBC Gateway: <strong>30th Aug 2017</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bihar Police Recruitment 2017', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bihar-police-recruitment-2017', '', '', '2017-08-04 06:38:41', '2017-08-04 06:38:41', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=291', 0, 'post', '', 0),
