(298, 1, '2017-08-05 10:48:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Government of Karnataka notified about Police Constable (FPM) recruitment open in Police Department. Candidates having PUC or equivalent qualification in Science having Biology , Physics, Chemistry, Computer Science, Electronics can participate in this recruitment project. Apply online from 24-July to 14-Aug-2017</strong></h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>KSP Vacancy Details</strong></h4>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n 	<li><strong>Total Number of Vacancies:</strong> 06 (six)</li>\n 	<li><strong>Salary Scale Offered:</strong> Not Mentioned</li>\n 	<li><strong>Application Last Date</strong>: 14-Aug-2017</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Eligibility Criteria </strong></h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n 	<li><strong>Educational Qualification :</strong> Candidates Must have PUC or equivalent qualification in Science having Biology , Physics, Chemistry, Computer Science, Electronics as one of the subjects.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Nationality :</strong> Indian</li>\n 	<li><strong>Age Limit : </strong>Lower &amp; Upper age limit is 19 to 25 years for GM &amp; 19 to 27 years for SC,ST,CAT-01, 2A, 2B, 3A &amp; 3B as on 14.08.2017</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>KSP Selection Process :</strong> The selection will be based on written test, Endurance, Physical Standard Test &amp; Viva Voce.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Application Fee : </strong>Candidates have to pay Rs.250/- for GM , 2A,2B, 3A,3B &amp; Rs.100/- for SC , ST, CAT-01, through<strong> </strong>in state bank of Mysore (sbm)/ state bank of Hyderabad (sbh) only. Candidates have to fill the application and generate the challan and make the payment in the respective bank.</p>', '', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2017-08-05 10:48:40', '2017-08-05 10:48:40', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=298', 0, 'post