(473, 1, '2017-09-19 09:08:14', '2017-09-19 09:08:14', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Government Organization</strong><strong>:- </strong>West Bengal Public Service Commission<strong>\r\n</strong><strong>Designation</strong><strong>:- </strong>Librarian\r\n<strong>Job Location</strong><strong>:-</strong> West Bengal<strong>\r\n</strong><strong>Application date</strong><strong>:-</strong> 20<sup>th</sup> September 2017</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Librarian</strong>:- 01 vacancy</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Qualification</strong><strong>:-</strong> Aspirants who wanted to participate for Librarian should have second class master degree in library science from a recognized university / institute or equivalent or a second class master degree in law subject other than library science plus a bachelor degree in library science from a recognized university / institute or equivalent.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Salary Structure</strong><strong>:- </strong>Rs 15600 – 39100/- Per Month</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Age Limit</strong><strong>:-</strong> Maximum 36 years as on 1<sup>st</sup> January 2017.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Selection Process</strong><strong>:-</strong>  Written Examination and after exams candidates will be invited for personal Interview.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Fee charges:- </strong>Applicants have to pay Rs. 210/- and Service Charge 1% of Examination Fee subject to a minimum of Rs. 5/- for online payment through debit/credit card plus 18% GST on convenience fee or Service Charge of Rs. 5/- only for Net Banking or Service Charge of Rs. 20/- only for payment through Bank counter (off-line payment). SC/ST candidates of West Bengal and Persons with Disabilities (PWD) having physical disability of 40% and above are not required to pay any fee.</p>', 'PSCWB recruitment 2017', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pscwb-re