(712, 1, '2017-10-10 09:40:20', '2017-10-10 09:40:20', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Organization Name:</b> Tamil Nadu Fisheries University (TNFU)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Employment Category:</b> Tamilnadu Govt Jobs</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Total No. of Vacancies:</b> 25</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><b>Educational <span id=\"IL_AD8\" class=\"IL_AD\">Qualification</span>: (As on 30.09.2017)</b></div>\r\n<div>1. Junior Assistant - 1) Bachelor Degree from a recognized university through 10 + 2 + 3 years system of education. 2) “Certificate course in computer on office Automation” awarded by the Directorate of Technical Education.</div>\r\n<div>2. Typist - 1. Minimum General Educational qualification. Preference will be given to degree holders. (a) Typewriting English Higher and Typewriting Tamil Higher (or) (b)Typewriting English Lower and Typewriting Tamil Higher (or) (c) Typewriting English Higher and Typewriting Tamil Lower. Explanation: Item (b) will be recruited if item (a) is not available and item (c) will be recruited if item (a) and (b) are not available. 2. “Certificate course in Computer on Office Automation” awarded by the Directorate of Technical Education.</div>\r\n<div>3. Steno-Typist Gr.III - 1. Minimum General Educational qualification. Preference will be given to degree holders. (a) Typewriting English &amp; Tamil Higher and Short hand English and Tamil Higher (or) (b) Typewriting English and Tamil Higher and Short hand English Lower and Tamil Higher (or) (c) Typewriting English and Tamil Higher and Short hand English Higher and Tamil Lower. Explanation: Item (b) will be recruited if item (a) is not available and item(c) will be recruited if item (a) and (b) are not available. 2. “Certificate course in Computer on Office Automation” awarded by the Directorate of Technical Education.</div>\r\n<div>4. Library Assistant - (a) Must be in possession of a certificate in Librarianship issued by the University of Madras or any other recognized organization; (b) Must have a good handwriting</div>\r\n<div>5. Fishery Assistant - (a) Minimum General Educational Qualification; (b) Must have undergone 10 months training in any Fisherman Training Centre organized by Tamil Nadu Govt. under State Fisheries Dept. / by TNFU through Institute of Fisheries Technology</div>\r\n<div>6. Farm Manager - B.F.Sc., degree with Overall Grade Point Average of 3.00 / 4.00 or 7.00 / 10.00 or its equivalent is essential.</div>\r\n<div>7. Electrician Gr. II - (a) ITI Certificate in the concerned trade; (b) Must have ability to read and write the regional language; (c) Must have previous experience in any electrical undertaking or engineering firm for a period of 3 years; (d) Must have a thorough knowledge of all electrical appliances with special reference to motor testing, battery repairing, armature winding, attending to the installations like electric motors giving connections to motors and starters etc. Explanation - Preference will be given to persons holding certificates in electrical engineering issued by private institutes like Chengalvaraya Nayakar’s Technical Institute, Madras and Government I.T.I.</div>\r\n<div>8. Mechanic Gr. II - (a) A certificate in Mechanical Engineering of the Chengalvaraya Nayakar’s Technical Institute, Madras / any other institute approved/ recognized by the Government of Tamil Nadu for a certificate in the appropriate trade of the I.T.I; (b) Practical experience in a workshop or a factory for a period of not less than 3 years and experience in repairs and maintenance of tractors, pump units and agricultural machinery.</div>\r\n<div>9. Lab. Attendant - a) Pass in III Form or VIII Standard; (b) Good Physique; (c) Must know cycling; (d) Experience of attending on fishes or aquatic animals or Laboratory</div>\r\n<div>10. Office Assistant - (a) Pass in III Form or VIII Standard; (b) Good Physique; (c) Must know cycling; (d) Experience in Office works such as entry of tapals, stitching of bills, Despatch of Tapals and other Office works.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Job Location:</b> Nagapattinam</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Name of the Post &amp; No of Vacancies:</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">TNFU Invites Applications for the Following Posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1. Junior Assistant - 7 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2. Typist - 3 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3. Steno-Typist Gr.III - 3 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4. Library Assistant - 2 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">5. Fishery Assistant - 3 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">6. Farm Manager - 1 Post</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">7. Electrician Gr. II - 1 post</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8. Mechanic Gr. II - 1 post</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">9. Lab. Attendant - 2 posts</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">10. Office Assistant - 2 posts</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Age Limit: (As on 30.09.2017)</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Candidate’s Age Limit Should not exceed SCA,SC/ST- 35; MBC/DC, BCM, BC-32 and OC-30. Candidates Relaxation in Upper Age limit will be provided as per Govt. Rules. Go through TNFU official Notification 2017 for more reference</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Last date for Submission of Application:</strong> 07.11.2017</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'TNFU Recruitment 2017 25 Junior Assistant Posts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tnfu-recruitment-2017-25-junior-assistant-posts', '', '', '2017-10-10 09:40:20', '2017-10-10 09:40:20', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=712', 0, 'post', '', 0),
