(741, 1, '2017-10-12 11:07:31', '2017-10-12 11:07:31', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Organization Name:</b> National Institute of Technology Tiruchirappalli (NIT Tiruchirappalli)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Employment Category:</b> Central Govt Jobs</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Total No. of Vacancies:</b> 177</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Job Location:</b> Tiruchirappalli</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><strong>Essential Qualifications:</strong></div>\r\n<div> (i) Detailed Educational Qualifications, Experience and other criteria for selection shall be as per the modified recruitment rules for Faculty in NITs. It shall be as per schedule E of the first statutes of the NITs (amendment statutes 2017) reference Gazette of India dated July 24th 2017.</div>\r\n<div>(ii) All new entrants shall have Ph.D. in the relevant / equivalent discipline and shall have First Class in the preceding Degrees</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>For All Engineering/Architecture Departments: B. Tech./B.Arch. or any equivalent degree AND M. Tech. / M. Arch. or any equivalent degree in relevant discipline.</div>\r\n<div>Candidates having Ph. D. Degree directly after B Tech. from reputed Institutions/Universities will also be considered, if other norms are fulfilled</div>\r\n<div>For Humanities/ Management/ Applied Sciences: B.A./ B.Sc./B.Com. or any equivalent undergraduate degree and/ or M.A./ M. Sc./ M. Com./ M.B.A./M.C.A. or any equivalent P.G. degree in relevant discipline.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><b>Department wise Vacancy</b></div>\r\n<div>1. Architecture - 9</div>\r\n<div>2. Civil Engineering - 19</div>\r\n<div>3. Chemical Engineering - 6</div>\r\n<div>4. Energy &amp; Environment - 5</div>\r\n<div>5. Chemistry - 9</div>\r\n<div>6. Computer Science Engineering - 11</div>\r\n<div>7. Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering - 14</div>\r\n<div>8. Electricals &amp; Electronics Engineering - 15</div>\r\n<div>9. Humanities 7</div>\r\n<div>10. Instrumentation &amp; Control Engineering - 8</div>\r\n<div>11. Mechanical Engineering - 14</div>\r\n<div>12. Metallurgical &amp; Material Engineering - 11</div>\r\n<div>13. Management Studies - 10</div>\r\n<div>14. Computer Application - 9</div>\r\n<div>15. Mathematics - 11</div>\r\n<div>16. Physics - 6</div>\r\n<div>17. Production - 13</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Last date for Submission of Application: </strong>11.11.2017</div>\r\n<div></div>', 'NIT Tiruchirappalli Recruitment 2017', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nit-tiruchirappalli-recruitment-2017', '', '', '2017-10-12 11:07:31', '2017-10-12 11:07:31', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=741', 0, 'post', '', 0),
