(761, 1, '2017-10-13 08:34:31', '2017-10-13 08:34:31', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Organization Name:</b> Bharat Dynamics Limited (BDL)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Employment Category:</b> Central Govt Jobs</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Total No. of Vacancies:</b> 51</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Job Location:</b> Hyderabad</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><b>Latest BDL Vacancy Details:</b></div>\r\n<div><b>Name of the Post &amp; No of Vacancies:</b></div>\r\n<div>BDL Invites Applications for the Following Posts</div>\r\n<div>1. Executive Director (P&amp;A) - 01</div>\r\n<div>2. Company Secretary - 01</div>\r\n<div>3. Dy. General Manager (P&amp;A) - 01</div>\r\n<div>4. Sr. Manager (Finance) - 01</div>\r\n<div>5. Manager (Finance) - 01</div>\r\n<div>6. Manager (Business Development) - 01</div>\r\n<div>7. Manager (Safety) - 01</div>\r\n<div>8. Dy. Manager (Safety) - 01</div>\r\n<div>9. Assistant Manager (Safety) - 01</div>\r\n<div>10. Manager (Civil) - 01</div>\r\n<div>11. Dy. Manager (Civil) - 01</div>\r\n<div>12. Dy. Manager (Electrical) - 01</div>\r\n<div>13. Dy. Manager (Electronics) - 10</div>\r\n<div>14. Dy. Manager (Finance) - 01</div>\r\n<div>15. Dy. Manager (P&amp;A) - 05</div>\r\n<div>16. MT (Electrical) - 02</div>\r\n<div>17. MT (Electronics) - 09</div>\r\n<div>18. MT (Computer Science) - 03</div>\r\n<div>19. MT (<span id=\"IL_AD9\" class=\"IL_AD\">Optics</span>) - 01</div>\r\n<div>20. MT (Finance) - 08</div>\r\n<div>21. MT (Company Secretary) - 01</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><b>Eligibility Criteria for BDL Vacancy 2017:</b></div>\r\n<div><b>Educational Qualification:</b></div>\r\n<div>1. Executive Director (P&amp;A) - First Class in MBA or equivalent / Post <span id=\"IL_AD6\" class=\"IL_AD\">Graduate Diploma</span>/ Post Graduate Degree in HR/ PM&amp;IR/ Personnel Management/ <span id=\"IL_AD7\" class=\"IL_AD\">Industrial Relations</span>/ Social Science/ Social Welfare/ Social Work of 2 years duration from University/Institution recognized by Government. +  20 Years Post Qualification Experience</div>\r\n<div>2. Company Secretary - Membership of the Institute of Company <span id=\"IL_AD10\" class=\"IL_AD\">Secretaries</span> of India. + Minimum 14 Years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>3. Dy. General Manager (P&amp;A) - First Class in MBA or equivalent / Post Graduate Diploma/ Post Graduate Degree in HR/ PM&amp;IR/ Personnel Management/ Industrial Relations/ Social Science/ Social Welfare/ Social Work of 2 years duration from University/Institution recognized by Government. + 05 Years Post Qualification Experience</div>\r\n<div>4. Sr. Manager (Finance) - Membership of the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) (OR) Membership of Institute of Cost and Works Accountants of India (ICAI erstwhile ICWAI) (OR) First Class MBA or equivalent /Post Graduate Diploma / Post Graduate <span id=\"IL_AD4\" class=\"IL_AD\">Degree in Finance</span> discipline of 2 Years duration from University / Institution recognized by Government. + 09 Years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>5. Manager (Finance) - Membership of the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) (OR) Membership of Institute of Cost and Works Accountants of India (ICAI erstwhile ICWAI) (OR) First Class MBA or equivalent /Post Graduate Diploma / Post Graduate Degree in Finance discipline of 2 Years duration from University / Institution recognized by Government. + 07 Years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>6. Manager (Business Development) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5-year integrated course) in Engineering or Technology (Mechanical/ Electrical &amp; Electronics/ Electronics &amp; Communications/ Electronics &amp; Instrumentation/ Industrial Electronics/ Production) AND First Class in 2-years MBA or equivalent / Post Graduate Diploma/ Post Graduate Degree with specialization in Marketing/ Sales &amp; Marketing awarded by Universities/ Institutions recognized by the Government + Minimum 7 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>7. Manager (Safety) - i (a) Degree in any branch of Engineering or Technology from a recognized University / Institute. (OR) (b) Graduate Degree in Physics or Chemistry from a recognized University / Institute ii) <span id=\"IL_AD5\" class=\"IL_AD\">Full time</span> Degree or Diploma or Certificate in Industrial Safety or equivalent of duration not less than one year awarded by any University incorporated under the Central or State Acts or Department of Technical Education or Board of Technical Education of any State Government in India. iii) Adequate knowledge of Telugu language is essential. + Minimum 7 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>8. Dy. Manager (Safety) - i (a) Degree in any branch of Engineering or Technology from a recognized University / Institute. (OR) (b) Graduate Degree in Physics or Chemistry from a recognized University / Institute ii) Full time Degree or Diploma or Certificate in Industrial Safety or equivalent of duration not less than one year awarded by any University incorporated under the Central or State Acts or Department of Technical Education or Board of Technical Education of any State Government in India. iii) Adequate knowledge of Telugu language is essential. + Minimum 5 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>9. Assistant Manager (Safety) - i (a) Degree in any branch of Engineering or Technology from a recognized University / Institute. (OR) (b) Graduate Degree in Physics or Chemistry from a recognized University / Institute ii) Full time Degree or Diploma or Certificate in Industrial Safety or equivalent of duration not less than one year awarded by any University incorporated under the Central or State Acts or Department of Technical Education or Board of Technical Education of any State Government in India. iii) Adequate knowledge of Telugu language is essential. + Minimum 2 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>10. Manager (Civil) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in <span id=\"IL_AD11\" class=\"IL_AD\">the discipline</span> of Civil or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute + Minimum 5 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>11. Dy. Manager (Civil) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Civil or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute + Minimum 7 years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>12. Dy. Manager (Electrical) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Electrical or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute + 05 Years Post Qualification Experience</div>\r\n<div>13. Dy. Manager (Electronics) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Electronics or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute + 05 Years Post Qualification Experience</div>\r\n<div>14. Dy. Manager (Finance) - Membership of the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) (OR) Membership of Institute of Cost and Works Accountants of India (ICAI erstwhile ICWAI) (OR) First Class MBA or equivalent /Post Graduate Diploma / Post Graduate Degree in Finance discipline of 2 Years duration from University / Institution recognized by Government. + 05 Years of Post Qualification Executive experience</div>\r\n<div>15. Dy. Manager (P&amp;A) - First Class in MBA or equivalent / Post Graduate Diploma/ Post Graduate Degree in HR/ PM&amp;IR/ Personnel Management/ Industrial Relations/ Social Science/ Social Welfare/ Social Work of 2 years duration from University/Institution recognized by Government. + 14 Years Post Qualification Experience</div>\r\n<div>16. MT (Electrical) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Electrical or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute</div>\r\n<div>17. MT (Electronics) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Electronics or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute</div>\r\n<div>18. MT (Computer Science) - First Class Bachelor’s Degree (or 5- Year Integrated course) in Engineering or Technology in the discipline of Computer Science or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute</div>\r\n<div>19. MT (Optics) - First Class MSc. Degree in Physics/ Applied Physics with specialization in Optics/ Applied Optics / Fiber Optics/ Laser / Optoelectronics or MSc.(Tech)-Engineering Physics with specialization in Photonics or equivalent course from a recognized University/ Institute</div>\r\n<div>20. MT (Finance) - Pass in Final examination conducted by Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) (OR) Pass in Final examination conducted by Institute of Cost and Works Accountants of India (ICAI erstwhile ICWAI) (OR) First Class MBA or equivalent /Post Graduate Diploma / Post Graduate Degree in Finance discipline of 2 Years duration from University / Institution recognized by Government</div>\r\n<div>21. MT (Company Secretary) - Membership of the Institute of Company Secretaries of India. • Desirable- Graduate</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Last date for Submission of Application: </strong>28.10.2017</div>', 'BDL Recruitment 2017 51 MT, Manager Posts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bdl-recruitment-2017-51-mt-manager-posts', '', '', '2017-10-13 08:34:31', '2017-10-13 08:34:31', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=761', 0, 'post', '', 0),
