(835, 1, '2017-10-26 12:23:06', '2017-10-26 12:23:06', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Organization Name:</b> Indian Army</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Employment Category:</b> Central Govt Jobs</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Total No. of Vacancies:</b> 40</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Job Location:</b> All Over India</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div>1. Civil. - 10 Posts</div>\r\n<div>2. Architectural. - 01 Post</div>\r\n<div>3. Mechanical – 4 Posts</div>\r\n<div>4. Electrical &amp; Electronics - 5 Posts</div>\r\n<div>5. Computer Sc &amp; Engg/Computer Technology/Info Tech/MSc (Computer Sc) - 6 Posts</div>\r\n<div>6. Electronics &amp; Telecommunication/Telecommunication/Electronics &amp;Communication/ Satellite Communication - 7 Posts</div>\r\n<div>7. Electronics - 2 Posts</div>\r\n<div>8. Metallurgical - 2 Posts</div>\r\n<div>9. Electronics &amp; instrumentation/Instrumentation - 2 Posts</div>\r\n<div>10. Micro Electronics and Microwave - <span id=\"IL_AD10\" class=\"IL_AD\">1 Post</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><b>Educational Qualification:</b></div>\r\n<div>Candidates who have passed the requisite Engineering Degree course or in the final year of Engineering Degree course are eligible to apply The candidate studying in the final year of Engg degree course should be able to submit proof of passing by 01 Jul 2018 and produce the Engg Degree Certificate within 12 weeks from the date of commencement of training at IMA. Such candidates will be inducted on Additional Bond Basis for recovery of the cost of training at IMA as notified from time to time as well as stipend and pay &amp; allowances paid, 1n case they fail to produce the requisite Degree Certificate within the specified time.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>1. Civil. - Civil Engineering, Civil Engineering (Structural Engineering), Structural Engineering</div>\r\n<div>2. Architectural. - Architecture Engineering</div>\r\n<div>3. Mechanical - Mechanical Engg, Mechanical (Mechatronics) Engg, Mechanical &amp; Automation Engg</div>\r\n<div>4. Electrical &amp; Electronics - Electrical Engg, Electrical Engg (Electronics &amp; Power), Power System Engg, Electrical &amp; Electronics Engg</div>\r\n<div>5. Computer Sc &amp; Engg/Computer Technology/Info Tech/MSc (Computer Sc) - Computer Engg, Computer Science. Computer Science Engg, Computer Science &amp; Engg, Information Science &amp; Engg</div>\r\n<div>6. Electronics &amp; Telecommunication/Telecommunication/Electronics &amp;Communication/ Satellite Communication - Electronics &amp; Telecommunication Engg, Telecommunication Engg, Electronics &amp; Communication Engg, Electronics &amp; Electrical Communication Engg</div>\r\n<div>7. Electronics - Power Electronics &amp; Drives</div>\r\n<div>8. Metallurgical - Metallurgical Engg, Metallurgy &amp; Material Technology, Metallurgy &amp; Material Engg, Metallurgy &amp; Engg &amp; Material - Science, Metallurgy and Explosives</div>\r\n<div>9. Electronics &amp; instrumentation/Instrumentation - Instrumentation Engg, Electronics &amp; Instrumentation &amp; Control Engg, Instrumentation &amp; Control Engg, Instrumentation Technology</div>\r\n<div>10. Micro Electronics and Microwave - Micro Electronics and Microwave</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Last date for Submission of Application:</strong> 22.11.2017</div>', 'Indian Army Recruitment 2017 40 Technical Graduate Course (TGC - 127) July 2018 Posts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'indian-army-recruitment-2017-40-technical-graduate-course-tgc-127-july-2018-posts', '', '', '2017-10-26 12:23:06', '2017-10-26 12:23:06', '', 0, 'http://successfulindia.aypt.in/blog/?p=835', 0, 'post', '', 0),
